OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Roy Hayward
OL,5,FRoy Hayward, Age 98, Sherwood Rangers
OL,6,FYeomanry
OL,8,FInterviewed 22 November 2023
OL,10,FDied 15 December 2024
OL,12,FLanding after dark on the evening of D-
OL,13,FDay on Gold Beach as a reserve tank
OL,14,Fcrewman, Roy Hayward from the Isle of
OL,15,FWight was in an ammunition lorry
OL,16,Ffollowing a line of tanks as it moved
OL,17,Fforwards.
OL,19,FHe said: "We left from Southampton on
OL,20,F6 June.
