OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Roy Hayward
OL,5,F"We landed in the dark that evening,
OL,6,Fand I was on Gold.
OL,8,F"Arromanches was the main part where
OL,9,Fwe were landing. We were already
OL,10,Fhaving a lot of casualties and so I
OL,11,Fwas called up to be the radio operator
OL,12,Fin the tank crew."
OL,14,FA few days later the Sherman tank Mr
OL,15,FHayward was in took a direct hit from
OL,16,Fan enemy shell.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
