OL,5,FHe said: "The left one just above the
OL,6,Fankle and the right one about five
OL,7,Finches below the knee.
OL,9,F"I don't think it had a lot of effect
OL,10,Fon me. I accepted it straight away. I
OL,11,Fknew that was going to happen.
OL,13,F"Particularly later I thought 'Gosh
OL,14,Fyou are so lucky you have come back. I
OL,15,Flost so many friends and members of my
OL,16,Fregiment who didn't come back.
OL,18,F"And that's been my attitude."
